Round-1 fixes:
1. Evaluator now fetches trial.branch (work/<slug>-<trial_id>) before worktree-add — chapter-3 §4 evaluator runs before integration so trial/* doesn't exist yet.
2. New §D.8a — ALL worker hosts use --bare clone topology (matches existing TaskWorktree). Startup refresh is 'git fetch --prune origin +refs/heads/*:refs/heads/*' which is bare-safe.
3. New §D.7c — orchestrator startup walks REMOTE trial/* refs via git ls-remote and store-authoritatively prunes any whose Store.read_trial has no trial_commit_sha. Recovery for the §D.6 step-4a-failed orphan-on-remote case.
4. Role-specific transport-failure mapping: implementer → status=error (chapter 3 §3.3); evaluator → status=eval_error (chapter 3 §4.4); integrator step-2 push fails → step-4b local rollback only.
5. Stale text swept: HTTPS → HTTP throughout, pytest.mark.gitea removed from verification, mode 0644 → 0755, option-(a) text removed (already settled in §D.4).
