   646	## Out of scope
   647	
   648	- **Gitea HA / multi-instance.** Single Gitea, single bare-repo
   649	  there. HA is a Phase 12+ control-plane concern.
   650	- **SSH or HTTPS-with-TLS instead of plain HTTP.** SSH key
   651	  management and TLS termination are their own follow-ups; plain
   652	  HTTP Basic is enough for the reference (Gitea is on the
   653	  compose internal network only; the same soft-boundary as the
   654	  existing reference posture).
   655	- **Gitea webhooks.** The orchestrator polls `Store` directly
   656	  for state; Gitea doesn't need to notify anyone.
   657	- **Multi-experiment Gitea.** This chunk creates ONE repo per
   658	  experiment, named after the experiment id. Coexistence of
   659	  multiple experiments on the same Gitea works naturally
   660	  (different repo names) but no special wiring.

